title: Autechre Move of Ten & Oversteps 5.1 DTS-HD MSTR BluRay by A
description:
This is a BluRay of Autechre's "Move of ten" and "Oversteps" converted from Stereo to 5.1 DTS-HD Master Audio format
using the ArcTan mode of SPEC, a software by http://surroundbyus.com.
The Bluray image is small enough to be burnt to a DVD-R or DVD-RW, in addition to BluRay disks.
But it will only play in either a standalone BluRay player or a PC equipped with a BD drive.
Converted and renastered by Arpegio.
Enjoy.
